title: MASTER BED-PRIVATE BATH-PRIVATE OFFICE-ALL BILLS INCLUDED
posting_body: ['Offering: Master bedroom with large closet, private bath and separate office space, rent includes electric, gas, water, lawn and maintenance and gives you access to all communal living spaces, shaded driveway parking and ample storage throughout house, garage and shed.', 'Location: East Dallas-Near the Arboretum', 'House Amenities:', 'Large mud/multipurpose room with Murphy bed', 'Office spaces', 'Automatic lights and Elfa unit shelving in all closets', 'Walk in hallway closet', 'Windows with professional coverings (keeps house cool in summer)', 'Ceiling fans in every room', 'Recently updated heating and A/C,', 'Recently updated washer and dryer', 'Ability to charge an electric vehicle', 'Kitchen Amenities:', 'Large basin sink with garbage disposal', 'Alkaline water tap in sink', 'Hidden trash and recycling', 'Ample counter space and storage', 'Island with storage', 'Breakfast nook with under bench storage', 'Laundry area with storage', 'Gas range', 'Fridge with ice and filtered water', 'Pantry with pull out drawers', 'Back Yard Amenities:', 'Wooden privacy fence', 'Patio', 'Gazebo with fans and lights', 'String lights along fence', '4 large garden beds', 'Compost bins', 'Garage with storage shelves and deep freezer', 'Storage shed', 'Trash chute in back fence', 'Considerations:', 'Must be comfortable with dogs-I have 2 medium sized dogs', 'Must be comfortable with children in house-I am a nanny', 'BIPOC and LGBTQIA2S+ friendly']
